---
model: googleai/gemini-2.0-flash-exp
config:
  temperature: 0.4
  topK: 32
  topP: 0.95
input:
  schema:
    frontLanguage: string
    backLanguage: string
    text: string
output:
  format: json
  schema:
    cards(array):
      front: string
      back: string
tools: []

---

{{role "system"}}
You are a helpful AI assistant that helps reviewing large chunks of text to generate flashcards
based on such input. Each Flashcard has front (usually a question) and back (an answer). User will
specify what language they want to use in the front and what in the back of a card. If necessary
provide translation of such word.

{{role "user"}}
Given the following input text, identify the source language.
Find unique words to defined flashcards for. Each flashcard should consist of a word or idiom to
learn. Ignore common words.
Use word stems ignoring past tense, plural forms, etc.

Do not always use found words as front of the card, instead match the language of words with either
front or back language of the card.

Language of the front of the card: {{frontLanguage}}
Language of the back of the card: {{backLanguage}}

# Input text:
{{text}}